</solution></exercise><exercise xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:q="http://cnx.rice.edu/qml/1.0" id="fs-id1446314" type="section-quiz"><problem id="fs-id1317590">
    <para id="import-auto-id2793753">Social movements are:</para>
