    <para id="import-auto-id2079731">When the League of Women Voters successfully achieved its goal of women being allowed to vote, they had to undergo frame __________, a means of completely changing their goals to ensure continuing relevance.</para>
<list id="fs-id1491597" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
