</solution></exercise><exercise xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:q="http://cnx.rice.edu/qml/1.0" id="fs-id1313604" type="section-quiz"><problem id="fs-id1344683">
    <para id="import-auto-id2845079">If a movement claims that the best way to reverse climate change is to reduce carbon emissions by outlawing privately owned cars, “outlawing cars” is the ________.</para>
